social_posts.post_text: Had a wonderful @drparraimplantcenter Holiday Party 🪅 last night with my family & amazing staff (and their family). I had the honor of visiting @dr.sheila_derm at @avantdermatology and I had such a wonderful experience. I was due for Botox but we went with the new @daxxify and I’m super excited for longer lasting results (6-9 months). I went home with lots of goodies including the new @upneeq eye drops that lift & open up the eyes for up to 8 hours. Another Vegas birthday in the books, it was very different with kids but it was actually a lot of fun. One of my most memorable birthdays yet. We ate good food, walked around a lot, people watched, shopped, & some some amazing shows. The kids made sure everywhere we went everyone knew it was my birthday and I loved it. I still don’t think Vegas is for kids and I probably won’t bring them back every trip but I’m really glad we brought them this trip. It was just what I needed, I can thank my husband enough for his thoughtfulness and love (much more than the material gifts) it’s always the intention and attention. I love you #forEver #vegas #vegastrip
